{"tid":1512244,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"大家有幾耐冇寄過信？","createTime":"2019-08-27T20:42:46.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-28T15:31:02.000Z","uid":178470,"like":10,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"4b5957cb54ea2ca28a805126e90569589f8d5e9a","tid":1512244,"uid":178470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-27T20:42:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b786e0dd96bb9699ac893fd27063fdfb66c5382a","tid":1512244,"uid":219216,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-27T20:44:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"975a6cd6bbb21b7c143ba63bb941b0345067acdf","tid":1512244,"uid":100760,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-27T20:46:48.000Z","msg":"支持，推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n香港人！還拖！往死裏打！<br />\n828國泰城+#Metoo，831民陣，<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">901開始無限期癱瘓機場<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">貨運</span></span></span></strong>，902三罷<br />\n全面批鬥警犬及其家屬！<br />\n㩒錢/換美金，經濟制裁中共！<br />\n全面杯葛tvb廣告商同藍絲企業！"},{"pid":"441c4f46ca67415f3f793a43ea60e66759283028","tid":1512244,"uid":123713,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-27T20:47:04.000Z","msg":"其實作為黃絲 [共產黨信唔過]真係3歲就識既常識黎<br />\n但就係太常識 好容易忽略左呢個point<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/znxxz6R.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fznxxz6R.png&h=298a1ff8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/UMaLaFb.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FUMaLaFb.png&h=1fecf1a9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: orange;\"><br />\n呢張文宣好簡單 message得一個<br />\n就係透過强調對共產黨既不信用<br />\n將中共塑造成全世界既敵人<br />\n</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n中共既敵人有好多個<br />\n1. 黃絲<br />\n2. 所謂中立 其實只係顧及自身利益 點會信中共<br />\n3. 淺藍好多都唔信任中共 只係無腦崇拜權威 實例就係當年就大把人偷渡落黎<br />\n4. 全世界其他民主國家盟友<br />\n<br />\n5.仲有個bonus<br />\n少數係大陸覺醒左既人 例如品葱上就有唔少<br />\n加上其他冇機會出聲既大陸人 （或者出左聲我地唔冇機會睇到）<br />\n佢地係日常生活遇到既不公義一定唔會少過我地<br />\n而黨媒又一定會大肆報導香港所有活動 <br />\n只要每個鏡頭都充滿住反共訊息<br />\n就可以透過黨媒向中國輸出對中共既不信用！<br />\n<br />\n黎緊831五周年<br />\n一人同我拎一張！！！！<br />\n<br />\n如果大家想既<br />\n仲可以印貼紙印滿成個香港！"},{"pid":"8bd2eb6cd4aa8960e3f94cd48fa8f426d5693880","tid":1512244,"uid":178470,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-27T20:51:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"53974130501bfadb3de9f201af0710589497c181","tid":1512244,"uid":23828,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"8bd2eb6cd4aa8960e3f94cd48fa8f426d5693880","tid":1512244,"uid":178470,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-27T20:51:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-27T21:34:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/censored.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8897dcb0fe45c9e18d08eb3634926e7f039f0cac","tid":1512244,"uid":283215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-27T21:37:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"814efc647a8a397a74b3b3dcb9054aaf24a6dbd4","tid":1512244,"uid":178470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8897dcb0fe45c9e18d08eb3634926e7f039f0cac","tid":1512244,"uid":283215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-27T21:37:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-28T05:42:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1077ef21132e418b850831a0e358b839c89a4f49","tid":1512244,"uid"